  "title": "Japanese Language Teacher",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Teach group and individual lessons for general and specific purposes</li>\n  <li>Teach on a face-to-face, blended and online basis</li>\n  <li>Teach at the school or the client’s office</li>\n  <li>Set and mark homework assignments</li>\n  <li>Monitor learners’ progress and produce reports</li>\n  <li>Administer and mark pre-course and post-course assessment tests</li>\n  <li>Organise and take part in social activities</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We’re looking for someone who:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>has a high level of linguistic competence in the target language (ability to use it and describe its grammar and vocabulary, but also use it in a manner that is appropriate for a classroom setting)</li>\n  <li>holds a high school diploma, university degree, equivalent or higher educational qualification</li>\n  <li>has good computer skills and is familiar with online teaching applications</li>\n  <li>is presentable, dynamic and proactive, and possesses excellent interpersonal and intercultural skills</li>\n</ul>",
